ore\": 0.9213795006400944, \"rank\": 0.08532873162707798, \"text\": \"Georgian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian-style Foreign Agents Lawadoptedby the Parliamentary Majority can be used to target any CSO and critical media, for any activity.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Civil_society_organization\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.144683328716442e-12, \"text\": \"CSO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Civil_society_organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Civil_society_organization\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its scope aims to stigmatise and silence all critical actors to the state authorities.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fines envisaged by the law are defined in a way that imposes massive financial sanctions on entities and individuals in an endless manner.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The non-payment of the fines can lead to the imposition of additional sanctions, including the freezing of assets.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The adoption of the law in the pre-election period is not accidental.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, the time was deliberatelychosenby the ruling political party.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Democratic security comes at a price.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Democratic security\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/